## Project identity

This is **glmocr-prod**: the AWS production deployment of a GLM-OCR document-OCR service. The local dev stack (Windows + Docker Compose + RTX 3060 Ti) has already been built, measured, and tuned; this repo is the port to Fargate + SageMaker + Go CDK.

**Architecture in one line:** a Fargate ECS service (CPU layout + OCR orchestration) calls a SageMaker real-time endpoint (SGLang GLM-OCR) through a task-local SigV4-proxy sidecar. Everything deployed via Go AWS CDK v2.

