## Tech stack

- **Infra:** AWS CDK v2 (Go). Target account, region, stage via CDK context (`--context stage=prod`).
- **CPU layer:** ECS Fargate (8 vCPU / 16 GB), x86_64, running `docker/cpu/Dockerfile.slim` (unchanged from dev).
- **GPU layer:** SageMaker real-time endpoint on `ml.g4dn.2xlarge` (T4, 16 GB VRAM), BYOC container wrapping `lmsysorg/sglang`.
- **OCR engine:** SGLang serving `zai-org/GLM-OCR` with NEXTN speculative decoding (aliases to EAGLE internally).
- **Layout detector:** PP-DocLayoutV3 via ONNX Runtime, numpy post-processing (Conv-dominated, ~1,100 ms/call).
- **Observability:** Grafana Cloud Mimir (metrics) + CloudWatch (SageMaker + ECS). Alloy sidecar in each Fargate task.
- **Secrets:** AWS Secrets Manager (`glmocr/prod/*`).
- **Config knobs:** SSM Parameter Store (`/glmocr/prod/*`).
- **CI:** GitHub Actions with OIDC. See `docs/prod/08-ci-cd.md`.

