## Tuned-knob cheat sheet

Authoritative copy: `docs/prod/reference/env-tuned.md`. Don't change these without evidence — each was picked from measurement on a g4dn-class CPU + a 16 GB GPU equivalent.

```ini
# CPU (Fargate task env)
CPU_WORKERS=4
CPU_THREADS=16
OMP_NUM_THREADS=1
MKL_NUM_THREADS=1
OCR_MAX_WORKERS=32
OCR_CONN_POOL=2048
OCR_RETRY_MAX=2
LAYOUT_BACKEND=onnx
LAYOUT_POSTPROC=numpy
LAYOUT_ONNX_THREADS=2
LAYOUT_BATCH_ENABLED=true
LAYOUT_BATCH_MAX=8            # don't exceed 8 — caused c=64 disconnects
LAYOUT_BATCH_WINDOW_MS=20
LAYOUT_ASYNC=false            # FastAPI sidecar didn't help; see memory
SGLANG_HOST=127.0.0.1         # always local — sigv4-proxy sidecar
SGLANG_PORT=30000

# SageMaker endpoint env (SGLang)
SGL_MAX_RUNNING_REQUESTS=64
SGL_MEM_FRACTION_STATIC=0.95
SGL_CONTEXT_LENGTH=24576
SGL_SCHEDULE_POLICY=lpm       # beats fcfs by 16-28% — don't change
SGL_SPECULATIVE=true
SGL_SPEC_ALGORITHM=NEXTN      # aliases to EAGLE internally
SGL_SPEC_NUM_STEPS=3
```

